---
import "../../styles/global.css";
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — MCZ">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-xl px-6 py-16 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg2">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-[32px] font-normal text-fg mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">What we collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">MCZ is a client-side tool. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Files you open in the Playground are processed entirely in your browser.</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">This site does not use cookies for tracking. If ads are displayed, third-party ad networks (such as Google AdSense) may use cookies to serve relevant ads. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We use GitHub Pages for hosting. Google Fonts are loaded for typography. These services may collect anonymous usage data per their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions, open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/nghyane/mcz" class="text-accent underline hover:no-underline">GitHub</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
